\v 1 Kodwa ngithi, ngaso sonke isikhathi indlalifa iseyingane, kayehlukananga ngalutho esigqilini lanxa ingumnikazi wakho konke\x + 3.29.\x*;
\v 2 kodwa ingaphansi kwabaphathi\x + Mat. 20.8.\x* lababonisi\x + Gen. 24.2.\x*, kuze kufike isikhathi esamiswa nguyise.
\v 3 Ngokunjalo lathi, lapho si\add se\add*yizingane, sasiyizigqili\x + 2.4.\x* ngaphansi kwemfundiso zakuqala zomhlaba\x + Kol. 2.8,20.\x*;
\v 4 kodwa kwathi ukuphelela kwesikhathi sekufikile, uNkulunkulu wathuma iNdodana yakhe\x + Mark. 1.15.\x*, yenziwa\x + Joha. 1.14. Roma 1.3. Fil. 2.7. Heb. 2.14,17.\x* ngowesifazana\x + Gen. 3.15.\x*, yenziwa\x + Joha. 1.14. Roma 1.3. Fil. 2.7. Heb. 2.14,17.\x* ngaphansi komthetho\x + Mat. 5.17. Luka 2.27.\x*,
\v 5 ukuze ihlenge abangaphansi komlayo\x + 3.13. 1 Pet. 1.18,19. Mat. 20.28.\x*, ukuze semukele ukuma kwabantwana.
\v 6 Njengoba lingamadodana\x + 3.26. Roma 8.15.\x*, uNkulunkulu wathuma uMoya weNdodana yakhe enhliziyweni zenu\x + Roma 8.9.\x*, ememeza \add esithi\add*: \w Abha\w**, Baba\x + Mark. 14.36. Roma 8.15.\x*!
\v 7 Ngakho kawuseyiso isigqili, kodwa indodana; njalo uba \add uy\add*indodana, futhi \add uy\add*indlalifa kaNkulunkulu ngoKristu\x + 3.29. Roma 8.17.\x*.
