\v 8 Kodwa ngalesosikhathi, lingamazi uNkulunkulu\x + Hlu. 2.10.\x*, laliyizigqili kulabo\x + Roma 1.25. 1 Kor. 12.2. Efe. 2.11,12. 1 Thes. 1.9.\x* abangeyisibo onkulunkulu ngemvelo\x + 2.15. 1 Kor. 8.4. 10.20.\x*;
\v 9 kodwa khathesi lokhu selimazi uNkulunkulu, yebo kangithi lisaziwa nguNkulunkulu\x + 1 Kor. 8.3.\x*, libuyela njani\x + 3.3.\x* futhi kumfundiso zakuqala ezibuthakathaka leziyibuyanga\x + Roma 8.3. Heb. 7.18.\x*, elifuna ukuba yizigqili zazo futhi kakutsha\x + 2.4.\x*?
\v 10 Ligcina izinsuku\x + Roma 14.5.\x*, lezinyanga\x + 2 Lan. 8.13.\x*\x + Kol. 2.16. Nani 28.11.\x* lezikhathi\x + 2 Lan. 8.13.\x*, leminyaka\x + Levi 25.2-5.\x*.
\v 11 Ngilovalo ngani\x + 2.2.\x*, hlezi ngitshikatshikele\x + Roma 16.6.\x* ize kini\x + 5.2, 4.\x*.
