\v 12 Banini njengami, ngoba lami nginjengani, bazalwane, ngiyalincenga; kalingonanga \add nga\add*lutho\x + 2 Kor. 2.5.\x*;
\v 13 liyazi-ke ukuthi ngobuthakathaka benyama ngatshumayela ivangeli kini\x + Roma 6.19. 1 Kor. 2.3.\x* ngokokuqala\x + 1.6.\x*,
\v 14 lokulingwa kwami okwakusenyameni yami kalikudelelanga njalo kalikwenyanyanga, kodwa langemukela njengengilosi kaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Sam. 29.9. Zek. 12.8. Mal. 2.7. 2 Kor. 5.20.\x*, njengoKristu Jesu\x + Mat. 10.40. 1 Thes. 2.13.\x*.
\v 15 Ngakho sasiyini isibusiso senu\x + Roma 4.6,9.\x*? Ngoba ngiyalifakazela ukuthi, uba kungenzeka\x + Roma 12.18.\x*, lalingakhupha amehlo enu linginike\x + Mark. 2.4.\x*.
\v 16 Ngakho sengibeyisitha senu ngokulitshela iqiniso yini\x + 3.1.\x*?
\v 17 Bayalitshisekela ngokungekuhle\x + 2 Kor. 11.2. Roma 10.2. 1 Kor. 12.31.\x*; kodwa bafuna ukulivalela ngaphandle, ukuze litshisekele bona\x + 2 Kor. 11.2. Roma 10.2. 1 Kor. 12.31.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa kuhle ukuthi litshisekelelwe kokuhle isikhathi sonke, njalo kungabi sebukhoneni bami lani kuphela\x + 2 Kor. 11.2. Roma 10.2. 1 Kor. 12.31.\x*.
\v 19 Bantwana bami abancane, engilomhelo futhi wokulizala\x + 3 Joha. 1.4. 1 Kor. 4.15. 1 Thes. 2.7. Jak. 1.18.\x* aze uKristu\x + 2 Kor. 13.5.\x* abunjwe\x + Roma 2.20.\x* kini\x + 2 Kor. 13.5.\x*,
\v 20 kodwa bengingathanda ukuba khona lani khathesi, ngiphendule ilizwi lami\x + Roma 9.3.\x*, ngoba ngididekile ngani\x + Joha. 13.22. Seb. 25.20.\x*.
\s USara loHagari bayimifanekiso yezivumelwano ezimbili
\p
\v 21 Ngitshelani, lina elithanda ukuba ngaphansi komlayo, kaliwuzwa yini umlayo?
\v 22 Ngoba kulotshiwe ukuthi uAbrahama wayelamadodana amabili; enye ingeyesigqilikazi\x + Gen. 16.15.\x*, lenye ingeyokhululekileyo\x + Gen. 21.2.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa eyesigqilikazi yazalwa ngokwenyama\x + Roma 9.7.\x*, kodwa eyokhululekileyo ngesithembiso\x + 4.28. Gen. 17.15-19. 18.10-14. 21.1. Heb. 11.11.\x*\x + Gen. 21.2.\x*.
\v 24 Okuyizinto ezingumzekeliso; ngoba laba bayizivumelwano ezimbili; esinye esentabeni iSinayi\x + Dute. 33.2.\x*\f + \fk iSinayi: \fl Gr. \fq iSina.\f*, esizalela ebugqilini, esinguAgari\x + 2.4.\x*.
\v 25 Ngoba lokhu, uAgari, kuyintaba iSinayi eseArabhiya\x + 1.17.\x*, njalo imele iJerusalema yalamuhla, futhi iyisigqili kanye labantwana bayo\x + 2.4.\x*.
\v 26 Kodwa iJerusalema ephezulu ikhululekile, engumama wethu sonke\x + Heb. 12.22. Isam. 3.12. 21.2,10.\x*;
\v 27 ngoba kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Thokoza, \add wena\add* nyumba engazaliyo; kekela umemeze, wena ongawuzwanga umhelo; ngoba abantwana botshiyiweyo banengi okwedlula kakhulu kulaye olendoda\x + Isa. 54.1.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa thina, bazalwane, njengoIsaka\x + 3.29. 4.23. Roma 9.8. Seb. 3.25.\x* singabantwana besithembiso\x + 4.23. 3.29. Roma 9.8. Seb. 3.25.\x*.
\v 29 Kodwa njengakulesosikhathi owazalwa ngokwenyama wamzingela yena ongowakoMoya\x + Gen. 21.9.\x*, kunjalo lakhathesi\x + 5.11.\x*.
\v 30 Kodwa umbhalo uthini\x + 3.8.\x*? \add Uthi\add*: Xotsha isigqilikazi lendodana yaso; ngoba indodana yesigqilikazi kayisoze idle ilifa kanye lendodana yokhululekileyo\x + Gen. 21.10. Joha. 8.35.\x*.
\v 31 Ngakho, bazalwane, kasisibo abantwana besigqilikazi, kodwa bokhululekileyo\x + 5.1.\x*.